Package org.thymeleaf.resourceresolver

Interface Summary
IResourceResolver Base interface for all objects used for the resolution of template resources (files, URLs, etc).
 

Class Summary
ClassLoaderResourceResolver Implementation of IResourceResolver that resolves resources as classloader resources, using ClassLoaderUtils.getClassLoader(Class) for obtaining the class loader and then executing ClassLoader.getResourceAsStream(String)
FileResourceResolver Implementation of IResourceResolver that resolves resources as files in the filesystem:
ServletContextResourceResolver Implementation of IResourceResolver that resolves resources as servlet context resources:
UrlResourceResolver Implementation of IResourceResolver that resolves resources as URLs:
